			description: [
				"&7\"No more manual labor with hammers.\""
				""
				"The &6Mechanical Press&f is your first machining tool. It uses rotational force to flatten ingots into plates."
				""
				"&eHow to use it:&f"
				""
				"Place the press above a solid block or a &bDepot&f."
				""
				"Supply it with rotational energy."
				""
				"Drop an ingot (Iron, Copper, Zinc...) underneath."
				""
				"&cImportant Note:&f In this pack, hammers have been removed. The press is now the &nonly way&f to obtain plates."
