			description: [
				"&7\"Some machines thirst for heat.\""
				""
				"You are going to need Lava in large quantities. Two schools of thought are available to you:"
				""
				"&e1. The Patient Method (Overworld):&f"
				"Place lava above a &bPointed Dripstone&f that drips into a &bCauldron&f. It's free, but slow."
